video_title: The Secret to Crafting the Ultimate Life!
transcript:
creating the life that you want and
achieving all of your goals only
requires three things Number One
Direction two action number three time
so ask yourself two questions every
single day and that's it number one am I
heading in the right direction number
two am I taking the right action and if
you are the only thing to do from there
is let God or the universe be in charge
of how long it takes to get there be The
Tortoise and not the hair because over
time you'll realize that slowly is the
fastest way to get to where you want to
be
